This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation and parallel corpus mining. It also involves the use of multilingual sentence embeddings, which falls under the category of natural language processing. 

It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the proposed method involves the use of embeddings and the improvement of existing methods through experimentation. 

Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the method involves retrieving relevant sentences from a large corpus. 

The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which could place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). 

Finally, the paper involves the use of image processing techniques for visualizing the results, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
